General.Name: Silk Logistics Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Silk Logistics Holdings Limited provides port-to-door landside logistics and supply chain services in Australia. It operates in two segments, Port Logistics and Contract Logistics. The company offers port logistics services, including wharf cartage; and contract logistics services, such as warehousing and distribution. It serves retail, fast moving consumer goods, light industrial, food, and other industries. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Port Melbourne, Australia.
